aking over 85 million shares of PT Indomobil Sukses Internasional Tbk (IMAS).", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "score": 65, "sector": "consumer-cyclicals", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/51657/manoj-dhamoo-punjabi-owns-pictures-film", "sub_sector": ["media-entertainment", "food-beverage", "investment-service"], "tags": ["Mergers & Acquisitions", "IDX", "Market Trends", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["FILM.JK", "NSSS.JK", "TRIM.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-12-05T11:46:36", "title": "Multiple investors make significant share purchases in various Indonesian companies across different industries."}, {"body": "Indonesia Stock Exchange authorities will improve stock investment literacy to increase awareness and prudence among retail investors, recognizing that all stakeholders have a responsibility to educate potential investors. This move comes after President Prabowo Subianto compared stock investment to gambling, highlighting the risks faced by small investors who are likely to lose out to bigger players.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 1, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "score": 65, "sector": "financials", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/51656/preventing-gambling-mindset-idx-continue-educate-investors", "sub_sector": ["holding-investment-companies"], "tags": ["IDX", "Market Sentiment", "Bearish"], "tickers": [], "timestamp": "2024-12-05T11:43:22", "title": "Indonesian Stock Exchange Authorities to Boost Financial Literacy Among Retail Investors"}, {"body": "PT Adaro Andalan Indonesia Tbk (IDX) debuted on the Indonesia Stock Exchange, with CEO Julius Aslan expressing optimism about the coal market's sustained attractiveness, citing solid demand from Asia and relatively high coal prices. The company aims to enhance productivity, reduce costs, and improve profit margins, despite acknowledging that market fluctuations are influenced by global conditions, particularly US-China political and economic tensions.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 1, "future": 2, "management": 1, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "score": 75, "sector": "energy", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/51655/us-china-tension-haunts-asian-coal-market-adaro-spoke", "sub_sector": ["oil-gas-coal"], "tags": ["IDX", "IDX Composite", "Market Trends", "IPO", "Bullish"], "tickers": [], "timestamp": "2024-12-05T11:31:23", "title": "Adaro Andalan Indonesia CEO Expects Coal Market to Remain Attractive Despite Global Uncertainties."}, {"body": "PT Multistrada Arah Sarana Tbk's (MULTI) go-private plan has yet to gain approval from independent shareholders, with only 24.59% of valid shares represented in the latest meeting, falling short of the required quorum. The company's free float is currently at 0.36%, well below the Indonesia Stock Exchange's 7.5% requirement, with Socgen SA Compagnie Generale des Etablissments Michelin holding 99.64% of the shares.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 2, "sustainability": 0, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "score": 75, "sector": "consumer-cyclicals", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/51654/masas-go-private-plan-stuck-whats-issue", "sub_sector": ["automobiles-components"], "tags": ["IDX", "IDX Composite", "Market Trends", "Mergers & Acquisitions", "Neutral"], "tickers": ["MASA.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-12-05T11:20:27", "title": "PT Multistrada Arah Sarana's go-private plan faces hurdles as independent shareholders fail to meet quorum requirements."}, {"body": "PT Bank Negara Indonesia Tbk (BNI) collaborates with Plataran Indonesia to present the Plataran Xtravaganza community festival, supporting the growth of Indonesia's creative industry and tourism, which can have a significant impact on the country's overall economic growth. During the event, BNI promotes cashless transactions, offering special promos to its loyal customers, and aims to increase awareness of environmental sustainability and contribute to advancing sustainable tourism.", "dimension": {"dividend": 0, "financials": 0, "future": 0, "management": 0, "ownership": 0, "sustainability": 2, "technical": 0, "valuation": 0}, "score": 65, "sector": "financials", "source": "https://www.idnfinancials.com/news/51653/bni-promotes-nusantara-culture-plataran-xtravaganza-borobudur", "sub_sector": ["banks"], "tags": ["IDX", "Market Trends", "Economic Reports", "Financial Ratios", "Bullish"], "tickers": ["BBNI.JK"], "timestamp": "2024-12-05T10:11:27", "title": "BNI and Plataran Indonesia Host Community Festival to Promote Nusantara Culture and Support Creative Industry Growth."}]